msgid "# Stop-Cluster"
msgstr "# 停止集群（Stop-Cluster）"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid ""
"Stops the Cluster service on all nodes in a failover cluster, which will stop all services and\n"
"applications configured in the cluster."
msgstr "在故障转移集群中的所有节点上停止Cluster服务，这将导致集群中配置的所有服务和应用程序也随之停止运行。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "### Cluster name (Default)"
msgstr "### 集群名称（默认值）"

msgid "### InputObject"
msgstr "### InputObject"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 描述"

msgid ""
"The `Stop-Cluster` cmdlet stops the Cluster service on all nodes in a failover cluster, which will\n"
"stop all services and applications configured in the cluster. A node can only function as part of\n"
"the cluster when the Cluster service is running on that node."
msgstr ""
"`Stop-Cluster` cmdlet 会停止故障转移集群中所有节点上的 Cluster "
"服务，这会导致集群中配置的所有服务和应用程序也停止运行。只有当某个节点上正在运行 Cluster 服务时，该节点才能作为集群的一部分正常工作。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1: Stop Cluster service on all nodes of the local cluster"
msgstr "### 示例 1：停止本地集群中所有节点上的集群服务"

msgid ""
"This example stops the Cluster service on all nodes in the local cluster, which will stop all\n"
"services and applications configured in the cluster."
msgstr "这个示例会停止本地集群中所有节点上的Cluster服务，从而导致集群中配置的所有服务和应用程序也随之停止运行。"

msgid "### Example 2: Stop Cluster service on all nodes of a cluster"
msgstr "### 示例 2：停止集群中所有节点上的集群服务"

msgid ""
"This example stops the Cluster service on all nodes in the cluster named `cluster1`, which will stop\n"
"all services and applications configured in the cluster."
msgstr "这个示例会停止名为 `cluster1` 的集群中所有节点上的 Cluster 服务，从而终止该集群中配置的所有服务和应用程序。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid ""
"Specifies the name of the cluster on which to run this cmdlet. If the input for this parameter is\n"
"`.` or it is omitted, then the cmdlet runs on the local cluster."
msgstr "指定用于运行此cmdlet的集群名称。如果该参数的输入值为`.`或被省略，则cmdlet将在本地集群上运行。"

msgid "Prompts you for confirmation before running the cmdlet."
msgstr "在运行该cmdlet之前，会提示您进行确认。"

msgid ""
"Runs the cmdlet without prompting for confirmation. By default the cmdlet will ask for confirmation\n"
"from the user before proceeding."
msgstr "直接运行该 cmdlet，而不会提示用户进行确认。默认情况下，该 cmdlet 会在执行前询问用户的确认。"

msgid "Specifies the cluster to stop."
msgstr "指定要停止运行的集群。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the time in seconds to wait for the cmdlet. If the **Wait** parameter isn't specified,\n"
"then the cmdlet waits for completion. If `-Wait 0` is specified, then the call is initiated and the\n"
"cmdlet returns without waiting."
msgstr ""
"指定等待该 cmdlet 完成的时间（以秒为单位）。如果未指定 **Wait** 参数，那么 cmdlet 会一直等待直到完成。如果指定了 `-Wait"
" 0`，则命令会被立即执行，且 cmdlet 会在不等待的情况下立即返回结果。"

msgid "Shows what would happen if the cmdlet runs. The cmdlet isn't run."
msgstr "展示了如果该cmdlet被运行时会发生什么情况。但实际上，这个cmdlet并没有被运行。"

